main event: A citizen in Colonia, New Jersey reported seeing a UFO on March 26, 1968 at 9:45 PM.
interesting points: The witness was 'cercely Radiant' after seeing the UFO.
The next day, the witness could not understand the meaning of what occurred.
The witness could not recall the calling time or those days.
The report indicates 'insufficient data' to draw a conclusion.
A follow-up AF Form 117 was sent to the witness on April 24, 1969 but had not been returned yet.
